# Project Structure Guide

- The main entry point is [index.js](mdc:index.js), which starts the server and loads configuration.
- The core server logic is in [game_server.js](mdc:game_server.js).
- All main source code is in the [src/](mdc:src/) directory.
- Games are implemented in [src/games/](mdc:src/games/), each in their own subdirectory (e.g., [src/games/lemonade/](mdc:src/games/lemonade/)).
- Utilities and shared logic are in [src/common/](mdc:src/common/) and [src/util/](mdc:src/util/).
- Tests are in the [test/](mdc:test/) directory and run via [testRunner.js](mdc:testRunner.js).
